data.text:
Dominique Hourani goes head-to-head with Maya Diab.

Sultry Lebanese singer, Dominique Hourani thought she had hit the big time when TV execs gave her the job of presenting a new primetime show on MTV Lebanon.

But it looks like the sexy songstress will be facing down some stiff competition in the form of "most stylish" star, Maya Diab .

Maya has been presenting her show, 'Hayk Minghani' (This is how we sing) every Saturday without a hint of competition but now that her rival has been taken on by the same channel, it looks like a cat fight could be brewing for the future.

2013 Al Bawaba (Albawaba.com)
